pros:
Intelligent, charismatic young professionals across the board;
Interesting events and access to top-dogs in DC and elsewhere;
Potential opportunities to get involved and have tangible impact.

cons:
Opportunities presented to staff depends solely on director;
Directors are not held accountable for their actions and, therefore, junior staff is treated poorly (open knowledge around the center yet no one does anything about it);
No on-boarding for junior staff which puts them at a disadvantage.
